title: Scrapheap Challenge - 01x04 - Off Road Buggies.avi
description:
This weeks' Yellow team consists of Major Dick Strawbridge, Kali Monroe, Dave Price and guest specialist Paul 'Yorkie' Zuckowskyj. 

The Orange team consists of Anne Saunders, Richard 'Bowser' Munson, Shen Chiu and guest specialist Mari Muench.

The challenge : build an all-terrain off-road buggy.

Help me seed (to a ratio of at least 1.5) & get these 'out there' - I have a max. upload speed of c. 80k/s. 

The more help I get the quicker everyone gets them. 

It's a team effort. So please, do your part.
